            "title": "1. Prepare the Garment & Spangle Transfer",
            "title_size": "heading-size--small",
            "seo_h_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_xMmipK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Pre-press garment for 2-5 seconds, this ensures fibers are flat and no wrinkles are present. Carefully peel off the transfer's backing, ensuring that only the spangle design remains on the clear adhesive sheet. Handle the transfer gently to prevent shifting or misalignment. Before applying, check that the design is intact and free from dust or debris to ensure a smooth and even press.</p>",
            "text_size": "regular"
          }
        }
      },
